# summary 
Smart Farming Advisor is an innovative artificial intelligence solution designed to help farmers increase sustainability and productivity. 
The project intelligently uses various data sources to optimize farm efficiency. The system monitors weather and soil conditions, 
analyzes plant health and evaluates market demands.
Using deep learning and machine learning, the Smart Agriculture Advisor can detect plant diseases and pests,
predict ideal harvest timing and provide informed recommendations to farmers. This solution helps farmers manage their resources efficiently,
increases profit margins and promotes digital transformation in the agricultural sector.
